articles.title: Alphabet: Time to Take Profits, Buy, or Wait for a Pullback?
articles.content: Alphabet (GOOGL) has experienced a significant stock rally in 2024, rising 76% from its 52-week low. While the company's fundamentals remain strong, technical indicators suggest the stock might be overvalued, prompting investors to consider waiting for a potential pullback before adding new positions.
articles.author: Ryan Hasson

articles.title: AirJoule Selected as Winner of Net Zero Innovation Hub Competition and Invited to Collaborate with Google, Microsoft, and other Industry Leaders on Water-Sustainable Data Centers
articles.content: AirJoule Technologies was named a winner of the Net Zero Innovation Hub competition, earning an invitation to collaborate with major tech companies on developing water-sustainable data center technologies that can harvest water from air with high efficiency.
